Invocation Name: port generator
des:
Ever have a hard time picking what port to run for your service?
Look no more.
This Alexa skill generates port numbers for the indecisive and the crafty.
If you want to change the default port or create a service where you want to pick a unique non-default port number, this skill will help.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
